trans-unit.source: Implements a set of predefined colors.
trans-unit.target: Implementa um conjunto de cores predefinidas.

trans-unit.source: The Windows Presentation Foundation color names match the .NET Framework, Windows Forms, and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)] color names.
trans-unit.target: Os nomes de cores do Windows Presentation Foundation coincidir com o .NET Framework, o Windows Forms e [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)] nomes de cores.

trans-unit.source: This representation is based on UNIX X11 named color values.
trans-unit.target: Essa representação é baseada em UNIX X11 denominado valores de cor.

trans-unit.source: The following image shows each predefined color, its name, and its hexadecimal value.
trans-unit.target: A imagem a seguir mostra cada cor predefinidos, seu nome e seu valor hexadecimal.

trans-unit.source: ![Predefined colors](~/add/media/art-color-table.png "Predefined colors")
trans-unit.target: ![Predefinido de cores](~/add/media/art-color-table.png "predefinido de cores")

trans-unit.source: Color Table including a color swatch, the color name, and the hexadecimal value
trans-unit.target: Tabela de cores, incluindo uma amostra de cor, o nome da cor e o valor hexadecimal

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Brush> class for a variety of other more complex ways you can color an area, including gradients (<xref:System.Windows.Media.LinearGradientBrush>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.RadialGradientBrush>) or images (<xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush>).
trans-unit.target: Consulte o <xref:System.Windows.Media.Brush> classe para uma variedade de outras maneiras mais complexas, cor de uma área, incluindo gradientes (<xref:System.Windows.Media.LinearGradientBrush>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.RadialGradientBrush>) ou imagens (<xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush>).
